XL cellular phones. The phones are regular Motorola
models featuring one-touch dialling, VibraCall
vibrating alert option, data capabilities, fast rapid
charging and headphone support.  A HATIS add-on is
available from Phoenix Management which plugs into
the headset jack on the phone.




