NETWORK BRIEFING via NewsNet
January 05, 1996

 INTERNET ACQUISITION COMPLETED


Boston-based Software Developer's Co Inc has completed
acquisition of Internet Security Corp, privately-held reseller of
security products for the Internet in a share swap valuing it at
$1.1m.

For the first half of fiscal 1996, Software Developer's achieved
record turnover of $26.6m, up 67%.

Internet Security did $175,000 net on $1.23m turnover for the
first half of fiscal 1996.






