C&W OFFERS LESS TO YOUNG

The board of C&W appears set to offer Lord Young rather less than he
wanted in terms of severance pay.  Young is thought to have been
looking for somewhere between #2.5 million and #4 million.  But C&W is
understood to have offered less than a year's salary plus his pension
entitlements, worth a total of less than #1 million.





