A new joint venture between AT&T, Rosnet (Russian Telecommunications
Network) and Intercon International of the USA is to provide data
communications services in Russia.  Structured as a joint stock
company, Rosnet International will purchase services and products from
AT&T and Rosnet while Intercon performs marketing functions.





