The London, UK METROPOLITAN POLICE are presently
taking a look at using the Internet for publicity
purposes... although they have no intention of
policing the information superhighway.  A steering
group has been set up with senior officers and
technical specialists to see how the service can take
advantage of the Internet's WWW. A number of separate
police stations and units have already set up their
own informal WWW services but a more formal Met
service is under consideration.




